<%= javascript_include_tag "https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js", async: true %>
<div id="order-options" team="" quantity=""> </div>

<section class="content-block pricing-table-2">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="underlined-title">
            <h1>It's Time to Show the World Where You Stand!</h1>
            <hr>
            <h2>Make your mark
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="tables-row">
                <div class="col-md-4 price-block">
                    <header>
                        <%= image_tag "instinct-sticker.png", class: 'img-responsive', style: 'background-size: contain;' %>
                        <h2>Instinct</h2>
                    </header>

                    <div class="features text-center">
                        <p>You heard Battery Bird's call and took up the cause. It's now time for you to share his noble message with the world using our 3" x 2.77" die cut vinyl stickers.</p>

                        <form class="form-horizontal">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="instinct-quantity" class="col-sm-4 control-label">Quantity</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                                        <select id="instinct-quantity" class="form-control">
                                            <option value="1">5 - $5.50</option>
                                            <option value="2">10 - $10.50</option>
                                            <option value="4">20 - $20.00</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>

                        <button id="checkout_instinct" type="button" class="btn btn-success">Buy Now</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 price-block">
                    <header>
                        <%= image_tag "valor-sticker.png", class: 'img-responsive', style: 'background-size: contain;' %>
                        <h2>Valor</h2>
                    </header>

                    <div class="features text-center">
                        <p>Tired of Team Mystic rolling through your gym like they own the place? Show them who's boss by marking your territory with these 3" x 3" die cut Team Valor stickers.</p>

                        <form class="form-horizontal">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="valor-quantity" class="col-sm-4 control-label">Quantity</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                                        <select id="valor-quantity" class="form-control">
                                            <option value="1">5 - $5.50</option>
                                            <option value="2">10 - $10.50</option>
                                            <option value="4">20 - $20.00</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>

                        <button id="checkout_valor" type="button" class="btn btn-success">Buy Now</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 price-block">
                    <header>
                        <%= image_tag "mystic-sticker.png", class: 'img-responsive', style: 'background-size: contain;' %>
                        <h2>Mystic</h2>
                    </header>

                    <div class="features text-center">
                        <p>Team Valor not paying attention to your philosophical rants? Confuse them with our high tech, gravity defying, dishwasher safe, 2.84" x 3" die cut vinyl stickers!</p>

                        <form class="form-horizontal">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mystic-quantity" class="col-sm-4 control-label">Quantity</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                                        <select id="mystic-quantity" class="form-control">
                                            <option value="1">5 - $5.50</option>
                                            <option value="2">10 - $10.50</option>
                                            <option value="4">20 - $20.00</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                        <button id="checkout_mystic" type="button" class="btn btn-success">Buy Now</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="basic-1-11" class="basic-1-11 content-block">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <h2>Quality</h2>
                <p>The stickers are die cut from a thick, durable, vinyl that has a UV protective laminate. This makes each sticker resistant to scratches and fading. The stickers are even dishwasher safe.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <h2>Taxes & Shipping</h2>
                <p>The sales tax, 8 percent, and shipping costs, $0.47, are an estimated at checkout. During processing the final tax rate is applied based on your shipping address.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <h2>Turnaround</h2>
                <p>Our expected turnaround time is about seven business days. Due to high volume of orders we can not give an accurate estimate. We will not charge your account until we are ready to process your order.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <h2>Support</h2>
                <p>Please contact us at <%= mail_to 'pokegraffiti@gmail.com' %>.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
